    "impact": "Any ERC20 tokens accidentally or forcibly sent to the global `ShareSale` or `BondingCurveSale` singleton can be stolen at near-zero net cost. The attacker can recycle the purchase payment through the fake DAO while extracting the singleton's preexisting token balance.",
